  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter single arm open label study. The primary objective is to evaluate the
      safety and effectiveness of the Lung Volume Reduction Coil (LVRC) for the treatment of
      patients with emphysema in multiple centers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
